<h2>The default — Google Classroom</h2>

<p>Every assessment in this course lands in Google Classroom unless you've pre-approved an alternative. The Classroom assignment for each deliverable specifies what to attach. If you're unsure where to submit, check Classroom first; if it's not there, ask Mr. Ignash.</p>

<div class="callout">
  <div class="callout-title">What you always include</div>
  <ul>
    <li>The deliverable itself — PDF, Google Doc, video link, slide deck. Whatever format the assignment specifies.</li>
    <li>Full citations for any sources you used (any consistent style — MLA, APA, Chicago, footnotes — pick one and stick with it).</li>
    <li>The <a href="/student-hub/ai-documentation-template/">AI Documentation Template</a> when AI was used. Which is almost always — assume yes unless you genuinely didn't open an AI.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

